high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the sink on the left.
Pick up the gray knife on the right of the salt shaker.
Turn right and move over to the front of the microwave.
Open the microwave and cut the apple inside into three parts.
Place the knife inside the microwave behind the apple.
Take out one piece of the apple from the microwave and close it.
Turn right to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the apple piece on the shelf between the glass bowl and white mug and take it out.
Turn left and go back to the front of the microwave.
Place the apple back inside the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cut piece of apple and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Move to the sink behind and do the left
Pick up the knife from the right of the counter and below the pepper grinder
Go to the microwave slightly to the right
Open the microwave and cut the apple inside
Put the knife in the microwave slightly behind the apple
Take a slice of apple and close the microwave door
Move to the fridge just to the right of the microwave
Open the fridge, place the apple inside, close the fridge door, wait, open the fridge, take the slice out and close the door
Go back to the microwave just to the left of the fridge
Open the microwave, put the slice inside and close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Preparing an apple and putting it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the microwave then turn left and walk to the sink.
Take the knife from the counter on the right side of the sink.
Turn around then go to the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave and cut the apple inside it.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Take an apple slice from the microwave and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on your left.
Put the apple on a shelf inside the fridge and close the door then open the door and get the apple.
Turn left and walk to the microwave on your right.
Put the apple slice inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled apple slice inside the microwave.
